# 🔄 FLOW الكامل للنظام

---

## 1️⃣ Transaction Manager (Safe Sale Execution)

```text
User creates sale
    ↓
Start DB Transaction
    ↓
Validate stock availability
    ↓
Check recipe availability
    ↓
Reserve inventory temporarily
    ↓
Process sale
    ↓
Deduct inventory + materials
    ↓
Commit transaction
2️⃣ Inventory Constraints Engine
Before sale:
    ↓
Check:
- product stock >= requested quantity
- material stock >= recipe requirement
    ↓
If NO:
→ Reject sale
3️⃣ Audit Log System
Every action triggers log:
    ↓
- sale created
- sale updated
- stock modified
- recipe changed
    ↓
Store full history
4️⃣ Accounting Ledger Engine
For every sale:
    ↓
Generate journal entry:
- Revenue (+)
- Cost (-)
- Materials (-)
- Profit calculation
5️⃣ Role & Permission Hardening
User action request
    ↓
Check role:
- Super Admin
- Admin
- Seller
    ↓
Check permissions per action:
- sale create
- sale edit
- stock adjust
6️⃣ UI Workflow Finalization
User Flow:
    ↓
1. Fast product search
2. Auto detect type (decant / full / unit)
3. Auto load pricing
4. One-click sale
5. Instant receipt
🧴 Example Full Safe Sale Flow
🧴 Lacoste White (5ml)
1. User selects product
2. System checks stock
3. System checks recipe
4. Starts transaction
5. Deduct:
   - 5ml perfume
   - 1ml alcohol
   - packaging
6. Save sale
7. Log audit
8. Commit transaction
💎 Dior Sauvage (Full Bottle)
1. Check full bottle availability
2. Validate stock
3. Deduct full batch
4. Deduct materials
5. Record ledger entry
